title: Daniel Craig shuts down reporter in excruciating Spectre interview after she repeatedly asks him to 'pout'
text: Daniel Craig shuts down reporter in excruciating Spectre interview after she repeatedly asks him to 'pout' Thursday, 22 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) An interview with Daniel Craig that aired on ITV's This Morning on Thursday has left viewers less than impressed, with some dubbing it 'embarrassing' and 'excruciating'.
